Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.11,0:00:03.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, all you viewers out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.95,0:00:07.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're watchin' Fairy Tail, make \Nsure to keep the room nice and bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.12,0:00:09.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and sit back from the screen, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.72,0:00:13.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.16,0:00:18.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A past comrade of Erza's, Jellal, is plotting \Nto resurrect Zeref using the Tower of Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.67,0:00:21.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We linked up with Sho and\Nother past friends of Erza's
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.38,0:00:24.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and somehow managed to defeat\NTrinity Raven of the Assassin's Guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.75,0:00:29.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But... Hurry, Natsu! Etherion is about to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.33,0:02:07.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is your real goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:12.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't really completed \Nthe R-system, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.84,0:02:17.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been doing nothing \Nfor these past 8 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.83,0:02:20.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I researched the R-system myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.54,0:02:24.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true there were no errors in the construction\Nor theory of the blueprints back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:30.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is something essential \Nmissing from the R-system.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.06,0:02:33.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, remember? You are the sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.16,0:02:35.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A problem more basic than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.43,0:02:38.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing you lack is... magical power!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.81,0:02:46.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A Prayer Under the Holy Light
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.83,0:02:55.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To activate a magical spell of this magnitude, \Nyou need a tremendous amount of magical energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.26,0:03:01.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you assembled every wizard on this \Ncontinent, I'm not sure it would be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.71,0:03:08.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So of course there is no way an individual \Ncould store enough energy in this tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.69,0:03:13.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And moreover, you know about the Council's \Nattack but are not trying to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.40,0:03:17.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:20.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Three minutes until Etherion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:21.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:24.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dream is already over!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.77,0:03:27.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you simply wish to die like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:29.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, then we go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.67,0:03:34.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not release this hand \Nuntil the final moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:37.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure... That doesn't sound too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:42.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My body was possessed by Zeref's spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.59,0:03:44.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No words will reach me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.35,0:03:49.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm nothing but a puppet used for \Nthe purpose of resurrecting Zeref.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:51.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Possessed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.51,0:03:53.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't able to save myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.14,0:03:58.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not friends nor anyone else could save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:04:04.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no Heaven... There \Nis no freedom, anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.99,0:04:09.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything was over before it even began.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.24,0:04:14.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Etherion, final firing phase complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.27,0:04:16.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Satellite Square, deploy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:19.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No problems with the transference lacrima!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:19.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Coordinates, locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:22.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No signs of rejection from elemental merger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.25,0:04:23.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin countdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:25.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us pray...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:27.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us pray...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:29.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us pray...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.14,0:04:30.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us pray...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:32.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:48.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That light!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.94,0:04:50.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Etherion!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:55.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, Erza... Hurry up and escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.72,0:05:01.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that the R-system wouldn't \Nbe able to be completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:05.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But the spirit of Zeref wouldn't let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:11.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late to stop it. I'm a \Nbroken engine that he's driving...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:15.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.34,0:05:16.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please put an end to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.84,0:05:20.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you came here, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.72,0:05:42.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no point in delivering the final blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.64,0:05:46.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Satellite Square is already deployed above.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.17,0:05:51.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over. For me... and you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.24,0:05:56.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Always the awkward one...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.57,0:06:00.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're also a sacrifice to Zeref, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.99,0:06:04.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my punishment for \Ngiving in to my weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.47,0:06:09.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart wasn't able to handle the \Nhuge gap between dreams and reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.27,0:06:17.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you have friends there to fill \Nin for your weaknesses and deficiencies?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:20.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:25.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am also repenting for my sin \Nof not being able to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.72,0:06:29.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.38,0:06:33.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:42.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us pray to the holy light!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.18,0:06:44.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Release Etherion!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:54.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:58.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu! Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.82,0:07:02.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This light...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.51,0:07:05.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:09.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:29.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.99,0:07:56.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Etherion has hit the target!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.54,0:07:59.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it successfully destroyed? \NHurry and confirm!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:02.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ethernano fusion density increasing! 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:04.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Predicting extreme weather patterns!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.38,0:08:09.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how many people were in that tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:16.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was to stop Zeref from being resurrected. \NTheir sacrifices were not in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:20.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether or not what we did \Nwas the right decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:24.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,that will not bring peace \Nto the victims' families.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:30.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.06,0:08:32.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu... Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.73,0:08:49.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.02,0:08:55.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:03.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ethernano neutralizing around explosion center!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.07,0:09:05.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.09,0:09:07.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fusion density dropping suddenly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.59,0:09:10.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A powerful, different magical \Nenergy is manifesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.60,0:09:11.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The gauge can't keep up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.77,0:09:12.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.76,0:09:14.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Restore visual!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:19.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crystal?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:21.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's magic crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:23.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lacrima!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.63,0:09:28.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, they're okay, right? \NNatsu, Erza, and Simon too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.11,0:09:37.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.12,0:09:42.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Etherion fired... So why am I still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:48.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally... Finally, the time has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.01,0:09:50.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.76,0:09:53.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the true form of the Tower of Heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.76,0:09:55.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a giant lacrima!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.96,0:09:58.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And thanks to the attack\Nby the Council's Etherion,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.53,0:10:02.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,it has absorbed an incredible\Namount of magical energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.65,0:10:05.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the R-system is complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:10.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The target is standing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:11.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A giant lacrima!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:15.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The lacrima absorbed the \Nmagical power from Etherion!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:16.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.48,0:10:23.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sieg... What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.34,0:10:28.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:44.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You tricked me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.38,0:10:47.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were really cute there, Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.93,0:10:52.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal was not able to produce his true power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.57,0:10:55.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He was in mortal danger, so he \Nhad no choice but to trick you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.39,0:10:57.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Siegrain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.76,0:11:15.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.46,0:11:19.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember the first time we met, Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:27.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That time you came with Makarov to deliver a \Nwritten letter of apology to the council, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:31.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You mistook me for Jellal and attacked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:34.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we look identical, so it's to be expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.47,0:11:39.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After you heard we were twins, \Nyou finally were pacified.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:42.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However you always treated me as your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.62,0:11:43.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.98,0:11:48.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of behaving as an older brother \Nshould, you tolerated what Jellal was doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:51.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, you were spying on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.43,0:11:52.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.80,0:11:54.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was my mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.95,0:12:00.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have said something like "I will find \NJellal and make him stop, no matter what."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.88,0:12:03.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I had finally become a member of the council,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.50,0:12:06.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so meeting you at all was my greatest mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.11,0:12:10.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The lies we tell in an unplanned \Nmoment cause us the greatest pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.10,0:12:15.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you two really did plot this together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:16.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Together?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:17.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.60,0:12:21.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it, Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.50,0:12:26.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We are a single person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.27,0:12:27.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,From the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.34,0:12:39.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.14,0:12:41.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A thought projection?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.29,0:12:45.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Siegrain is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:49.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you, yourself, fired Etherion?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.14,0:12:51.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you infiltrated the Council?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:55.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you enjoy your fleeting freedom, Erza?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:59.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything went according to \NZeref's scenario for resurrection.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:04.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You fiend... How many people \Nhave you deceived in your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.43,0:13:06.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Power...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.34,0:13:10.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...my magical power has returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.30,0:13:14.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A tremendous magical power is \Nbuilding in the Tower of Heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.26,0:13:17.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If that magical power is held \Nin one place it'll explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.15,0:13:19.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We were had.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.03,0:13:24.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:27.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The building is suddenly aging!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.11,0:13:29.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lost Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.13,0:13:30.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Time Ark?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.54,0:13:44.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultear...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:49.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is for Lord \NSieg... I mean, Lord Jellal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.69,0:13:55.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, his dream is being fulfilled!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.18,0:13:59.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the R-system?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:04.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's the true form of \Nthe R-system we built, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.22,0:14:07.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's activating...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.12,0:14:10.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Activating? You mean it's resurrecting Zeref?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.73,0:14:15.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. We've never seen it operate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:18.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And Natsu and Erza are inside of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.57,0:14:22.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Simon as well... And, Jellal...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.64,0:14:29.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your previous strength?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.46,0:14:33.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you use up too much of your magical \Npower in the battle with Ikaruga?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:38.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:49.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now the Council should \Nbe completely paralyzed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.37,0:14:52.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I must be grateful to Ultear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.54,0:14:55.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She did quite well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.67,0:15:00.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She said, "If in heaven all are seen as \None, then we need not fear even death."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.51,0:15:08.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For my ideal, for my dream, she said \Nshe'd gladly lay down her own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:15.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I truly must be thankful \Nto be given stupid women!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.11,0:15:16.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You fiend!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.66,0:15:23.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You should die from the curses \Nof all those you've used!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.84,0:15:28.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.15,0:15:30.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bind Snake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.21,0:15:33.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I put it on you when we hugged before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.09,0:15:41.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have the magical power \Nto activate the R-system.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.06,0:15:44.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All I need now is the human \Nsacrifice to resurrect Zeref.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:50.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no more time to play with you, Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.46,0:15:54.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The tremendous amount of magical \Npower this lacrima now stores,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.61,0:15:57.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,will be fused into your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.05,0:16:03.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your body will be deconstructed, \Nand then reconstituted into Zeref's.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:14.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I loved you, Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:17.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:25.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,O Great Zeref...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:30.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I give to you this woman's body!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.16,0:16:35.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.14,0:16:39.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:44.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.49,0:16:51.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza is a Fairy Tail wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.68,0:16:53.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't have her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:16:58.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.88,0:17:01.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.38,0:17:04.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.22,0:17:08.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to get back and do some work, \Nor the rent won't get paid this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.41,0:17:09.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy's rent, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.37,0:17:12.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.50,0:17:13.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.78,0:17:16.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You used to work me over pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:18.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So take some of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.80,0:17:24.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, get away from here as soon as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:25.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:28.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't do it, then I'll do it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.73,0:17:31.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop. He's got the advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.16,0:17:33.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know enough about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.56,0:17:35.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So I can't win unless I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.40,0:17:39.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:44.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.92,0:17:47.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, I don't know anything about you either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.33,0:17:50.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.64,0:17:59.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're even more outrageous than the rumors say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.02,0:18:04.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Had enough of hurting your \Nfriend when she can't move?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.53,0:18:05.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:09.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...was crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.56,0:18:14.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She was giving up...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:18.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And her voice was shaking...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.55,0:18:21.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to see Erza like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.92,0:18:24.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza should be strong and ferocious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.39,0:18:31.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want her to be her usual self when \Nshe wakes up from this nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:36.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:43.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting! Show me the dragon wizard's power!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:18:58.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wing Slash of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.64,0:19:01.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.68,0:19:02.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Talons!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.93,0:19:06.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:26.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you being serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.71,0:19:33.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu Dragneel... The child of Igneel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.45,0:19:42.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to taste the destructive power \Nof a Dragon Slayer before I destroyed you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:45.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but this is nothing to fear at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.41,0:19:47.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:50.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you interrupt the ceremony...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.56,0:19:53.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will use my Heavenly Body \NMagic to tear you to shreds!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.91,0:19:54.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Meteor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.25,0:20:06.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! He's too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:09.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't follow him with my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.22,0:20:13.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Smell, sound, feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.39,0:20:15.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Predict his movements... Concentrate...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:16.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Concentrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.58,0:20:20.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.84,0:20:23.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's even faster?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.89,0:20:29.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your attacks will never hit me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:42.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end. I will show \Nyou true destructive magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.63,0:20:48.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Be judged under the seven stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.63,0:20:50.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven Star Blades!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.58,0:20:52.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Chariot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.32,0:21:08.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a spell that destroys \Nwith the power of falling meteors.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:10.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed your body is still intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.24,0:21:13.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I went a bit overboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.99,0:21:18.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be dangerous to damage \Nthe R-system any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.20,0:21:20.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The magical power is starting to leak out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.73,0:21:24.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I must hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.06,0:21:28.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Erza?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.98,0:21:53.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That attack hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:58.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So breaking this tower, or um, \Nlacrima... That's bad, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.58,0:22:02.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Rotten luck for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.33,0:22:04.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.38,0:22:10.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Breaking things happens to be \NFairy Tail wizards' specialty!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.54,0:22:15.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all fired up! More than I've ever been!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.49,0:22:19.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.16,0:23:59.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, Etherion has started \Ngoing out of control!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.12,0:24:00.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate everyone will be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.16,0:24:03.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! There must be a way!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.72,0:24:05.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.11,0:24:07.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Throwing your body into the lacrima?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.53,0:24:11.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she attempting to fuse with Etherion \Nand stop it from going out of control?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.53,0:24:13.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.88,0:24:16.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Titania Falls
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.89,0:24:18.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.85,0:24:21.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't accept it! I won't accept it, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.98,0:24:24.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.44,0:24:26.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
